dct_alternative_sm: Descrittione della Palestina, o della Terra Santa, insieme con quella della Fenicia, lei vicina Palaestina vel Terra Sancta
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, travel routes, places of historical interest.
Descriptive text within a decorative cartouche and below map: La Palestina...
Appears in Ptolemaeus, Claudius, Geographia, Venezia Giovanni Battista & Giorgio Galignani, 1598.
